      <h1>Senior administrative staff</h1> 
      <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
       <div class="pageDescription"><p><strong>Secretary General</strong></p>
<table border="0" width="100%">
<tbody>
<tr valign="top">
<td><img alt="" src="/upload/FD/Portrettbilder/Depraad_Lund-Eriksen_100x150.jpg" /></td>
<td></td>
<td>
<p><u></u>&nbsp;</p>
<p><u><br />Erik Lund-Isaksen<br /></u>The Secretary General is the Ministry’s most senior permanent civil servant, whose principal task is to advise and relieve the Minister's running and coordinating of the Ministry.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><br />
<p><strong>Chief of Defence</strong><br /><u>Harald Sunde<br /></u>The Chief of Defence now has a dual role as both the Ministry’s most senior professional military adviser as well as being Head of the Armed Forces’ military organisation.</p>
<p><strong>Deputy&nbsp;Secretary General</strong><br /><u>Morten Tiller</u><br />The Secretary General is assisted by a&nbsp;Deputy Secretary General. In addition, the&nbsp;Deputy Secretary General assumes the role of National Armaments Director. In this capacity he coordinates the Ministry's materiel procurement activities, represents Norway in relevant national and international fora, and acts as a point of contact for Norwegian and international industry. </p>
<p><strong>The Director Generals</strong></p>
<p><u>The Department of Personnel and General Services<br /></u>Director General Gisle Norheim<br />Telephone: +47 23 09 61 00</p>
<p><u>The Department of Security Policy<br /></u>Director General Svein Efjestad<br />Telephone: +47 23 09 62 00</p>
<p><u>The Department for Finance and Management<br /></u>Director General Fridthjof Søgaard<br />Telephone: +47 23 09 65 00</p>
<p><u>The Department of Defence Policy and Long-Term Planning<br /></u>Rear Admiral&nbsp;Arne Røksund<br />Telephone: +47 23 09 64 00</p> </div>       
    </div>
    
               
        
    
